data.description: Great location and low HOA! Recently renovated, this 3-bed 2-bath home is move in ready. Centrally located and close to all major shopping. Once inside, you'll find vaulted ceilings, beautiful light features, solid countertops in the kitchen and on bathroom vanities, as well as tastefully selected and well installed laminated floors throughtout the house. Large walk in closet in owner's suite with plenty of room for the couple's clothes. This house is hitting the market in time for the family to enjoy summer BBQs while in the private and pavered patio, and under the gazebo equipped with solid countertops and a grill. Just near by, beautiful natural parks, a golf course, public docks, and fishing piers on the waters of the St Johns. This house has it all and is a must see!
